OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,FA woman who says she has been left in
OL,7,Fconstant pain after a surgeon carried
OL,8,Fout multiple harmful procedures on her
OL,9,Fhas spoken of feeling "violated" and
OL,10,F"cheated".
OL,12,FTracey Hanman, from Melksham, is one
OL,13,Fof hundreds of people who claimed they
OL,14,Fwere harmed after being given a mesh
OL,15,Foperation by Anthony Dixon, a leading
OL,16,Fpelvic surgeon.
OL,18,FA review by the North Bristol NHS
OL,19,FTrust previously found 203 women on
OL,20,Fwhom Mr Dixon performed procedures
OL,21,Fbetween 2007 and 2017 came to harm.
