OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1721386669
OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,F"He was quite convincing that that was
OL,7,Fthe best and only option for me," she
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,FAfter the operation, Ms Hanman said
OL,11,Fher pain started getting worse but
OL,12,Fwhen she returned to Mr Dixon for a
OL,13,Ffollow-up appointment, he dismissed
OL,14,Fher concerns.
OL,16,F"I just felt, just really stupid. He
OL,17,Fmade me feel really stupid, and just
OL,18,Fwasn't listening to anything I was
OL,19,Fsaying," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
