OL,3,CWoman left in constant pain after
OL,4,Cdoctor carried out harmful surgery
OL,6,F"He didn't need to do that surgery and
OL,7,Fa professional, that he should have
OL,8,Fbeen, would have known that so from my
OL,9,Fpoint of view, he just did it on
OL,10,Fpurpose.
OL,12,F"It felt like you were a guinea pig
OL,13,Fand you were just used for making
OL,14,Fmoney on. It was horrific."
OL,16,FMs Hanman said she has had to have
OL,17,Ffurther surgery in 2022 to have the
OL,18,Fmesh removed which has relieved some
OL,19,Fof her pain, but the operation has
OL,20,Fchanged her life forever.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
