OL,6,F"The tribunal has accepted the many
OL,7,Fsupportive testimonials received from
OL,8,Fnumerous patients of mine as well as
OL,9,Fmy former colleagues."
OL,11,FNeither North Bristol NHS Trust or
OL,12,FSpire Hospital Bristol comment on
OL,13,Findividual cases.
OL,15,FHowever in a statement a Spire
OL,16,Fspokesperson apologised "to all
OL,17,Fpatients whose care with Mr Dixon fell
OL,18,Fbelow the standards that should have
OL,19,Fbeen provided".
