OL,6,FThey added Mr Dixon was suspended in
OL,7,F2017 and has not worked there since,
OL,8,Fsaying: "We also referred Mr Dixon to
OL,9,Fthe GMC and worked closely with the
OL,10,FGMC in its investigations."
OL,12,FNorth Bristol NHS Trust's Chief
OL,13,FMedical Officer Tim Whittlestone told
OL,14,FITV News Mr Dixon was dismissed in
OL,15,F2019.
OL,17,F"We have carried out a thorough and
OL,18,Frobust review of affected patients,
OL,19,Fand would like to reiterate our
OL,20,Fapology to all of these individuals,"
OL,21,Fhe added.
